This is my custom desktop environment, that I use on most of my machines.

# Components

## patched suckless software
- [dwm](https://dwm.suckless.org)
- [dmenu](https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu)
- [slock](https://tools.suckless.org/slock)
- [st](https://tools.suckless.org/st)

## my own software
- bedstatus
- xbgcd
- pinentry-dmenu2
- netris (fork of NetBSD's tetris(6))
- various scripts
- my personal dotfiles
- /etc files

# Build Dependencies
- libX11
- libXext
- libXft
- libXinerama
- libXrandr
- libXrender
- libfontconfig
- libfreetype2

# Optional Runtime Dependencies
- font-awesome (for icons in bedstatus)
- htop (Super+Ctrl+H)
- libqalculate (Super+C)
- password-store
- xdotool

# Installation
First install all dependencies.

 $ make
 # make install
